---

Derived from the `writing-plans` skill in
https://github.com/obra/superpowers (skills/writing-plans/), with
modifications to emit a beans hierarchy (epic / feature / task) when the
`beans` CLI is available on PATH, falling back to the upstream markdown plan
output when it is not. The subagent-driven-development and executing-plans
handoff prompts from upstream are omitted in this fork because the beans tree
is the handoff.
